            "text": {
                "headline": "<a href='/class/2017/06/26/intro/'>Welcome to INLS161!</a>",
                "text": "<p>This is a course about pushing our boundaries and learning new things. \nIt is also about learning new ways of doing things that we might already know how to do. \nSome of the topics and skills covered by the course might be old hat for some of you. \nOthers may not have ever heard of some of these things. </p>"
            },
