            "text": {
                "headline": "<a href='/class/2017/06/27/clients-servers/'>Clients and Servers</a>",
                "text": "<p>Today we&#39;ll talk about some of the basic ways that computers work and\ninteract with one another. We&#39;ll also begin discussing the history of\ncomputing in the context of operating systems, UNIX, and Linux.</p>\n\n<p>In class we will also start with some hands-on-keyboards practice with\nmoving around the shell and manipulating files. </p>"
            },
            "unique_id": "2017-06-27-clients-and-servers",
            "group": "class"
               
