            "text": {
                "headline": "<a href='/class/2017/06/29/networks/'>Networks</a>",
                "text": "<p>We&#39;ve discussed a bit about how servers and clients operate. \nNow we&#39;ll look at what happens when we put lots of servers and lots of clients together. </p>"
            },
            "unique_id": "2017-06-29-networks",
            "group": "class"
               
