                "headline": "<a href='/class/2017/06/30/version-control-continued-lab/'>Version Control Continued</a>",
                "text": "<p>Today we&#39;re going to learn how to fork, clone, and push changes to a repository on GitHub using git. \nWe do this in preparation for creating personal websites that will be hosted by GitHub pages. </p>"
